<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi>
<lb n="2"/>kovirā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ke
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha">sa</hi>ripaṉmaṟku
<lb n="4"/>yāṇṭu 10 Ā
<lb n="5"/>vatu kuṉṟakkūṟṟa
<lb n="6"/>ttu<hi rend="grantha">brahmade</hi>ya
<lb n="7"/>m ciṟupaḻuvūrt ti
<lb n="8"/>ruvālantuṟai<hi rend="grantha">maha</hi>
<lb n="9"/><hi rend="grantha">de</hi>varkku nontāvi
<lb n="10"/>ḷakku Oṉ<unclear>ṟ</unclear>ṟu <unclear>Eri</unclear>ya
<lb n="11"/>paḻuvūr nakaṉ kāṭa
<lb n="12"/>nār iv ‡ vūr<hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yār vacam
<lb n="13"/>kuṭutta ‡ cāvāmuvā perāṭu
<lb n="14"/>90 ‡ Ittoṇṇūṟu
<lb n="15"/>Āṭṭā ‡ lum nicatam nārā
<lb n="16"/>yattā ‡ l Uḻakku ney aṭ
<lb n="17"/>ṭuvo ‡ m Ānom [[Icciṟu]]
<lb n="18"/>paḻu ‡ vūr<hi rend="grantha">sabhai</hi>yom <unclear>I</unclear>
<lb n="19"/>tu pa<hi rend="grantha">nma ‡ heśvara </hi><unclear><hi rend="grantha">rakṣai</hi></unclear>
</p>

